               <provenance>The name of the original donor was erased
                     throughout the Ms. and replaced with those of Walda Krǝstos and Fǝqǝrtä Māryām,
                     which in turn have been crossed out or were overwritten and replaced with those
                     of Walatta Bǝrhān and ʿƎśśetä Māryām (e.g., 13ra,
                     19vb, 39rb, 44vb, 47vb, 56ra, 66rb). Walda Krǝstos is mentioned as the
                     commissioner in Additio 1.</provenance></history>
